# Domain Knowledge Base

Before adding use cases, ports, endpoints, or business logic:

1. Read `docs/INDEX.md` and `docs/OWNERSHIP.md`
2. Read `docs/domains/<module>/` for the target NestJS module
3. For cross-repo work, read `docs/contracts/`
4. For FastAPI/embedding, read `docs/services/fastapi/` or `docs/services/embedding/`
5. For frontend API consumers, read `docs/contracts/frontend-api-map.md`

## Anti-duplication rules

- Do not duplicate logic already in a use case — extend the use case or add a port out
- Do not implement CV parsing, UPP runtime, or embedding index in NestJS
- Do not copy OpenAPI schemas into markdown — link Swagger instead

## Maintenance

When business rules change, update the relevant `docs/domains/<module>/` file using templates in `docs/_templates/`.
